--| [2] http://www/runtime/doc/gc.html
--| [3] http://cvs.gnome.org/lxr/source/gtk+/docs/refcounting.txt
--| [4] http://cvs.gnome.org/lxr/source/gtk+/gtk/gtkobject.c
